Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Ford shakes up team
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03z97q1
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 16 Nov 1975
President Ford sharpens his advisory team as the line-up for the next presidential nomination begins. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less